 where $\\Gamma\\sim {\\cal{O}}(1)$ is the\nLorentz factor of the bulk flow of the lava, which may be determined from the\nexisting GRB data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 18 Jan 2013 23:31:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 21 Feb 2013 15:53:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
